web2board (3.0.1) trusty; urgency=medium

  * Fix unhandled exception in asynchronous task when no board is connected.
    SerialMonitorHub.find_board_port now returns a BOARD_NOT_READY reply
    instead of raising CompilerException, and get_available_ports returns an
    empty list on error. Avoids the "No port found" traceback in the console.

 -- bitbloq Team <support-bitbloq@bq.com>  Thu, 16 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0100

